ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This class allows you to push boundaries and understanding of Russian culture. Just be sure to do your readings and prepare for discussion.

General course on Soviet literature and film of the 20s and 30s which will introduce students to the most significant works of the period. Recommended to anyone interested in 20s century Soviet culture.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It really helped me understand graduate level of thinking and pushed me to new academic extremes!
Helpful for Slavic exams on the 20s century literature as well as Oral field exam on Russian/Soviet film.
